        <a href="/chat" class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">ğŸ’¬</span> Chat</a>
        <a href="/profile" class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">ğŸ‘¤</span> Profil</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>